# Features[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#features)

[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#features)
Explore the powerful capabilities of FusionPBX, organized into categories below. Each feature links to detailed documentation where available.

## Call Management[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#call-management)
[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#call-management)
Feature
Description
Documentation
Announcements
Set up auto attendant recordings for caller announcements
[IVR Menus](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/ivr.html)
Barge/Eavesdrop/Intercept
Listen into active calls from another extension
[Feature Codes](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/additional_information/feature_codes.html)
Call Block
Block inbound calls by caller ID
[Call Block](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/call_block.html)
Call Broadcast
Create a recording and select one or more groupsto have the system call and play the recording
[Call Broadcast](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/call_broadcast.html)
Call Forward
Forward calls to extensions or external numbers
[Call Routing](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/call_routing.html)
Call Monitoring
View which extensions are currently in a call(see [Active Extensions](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#../status/active_extensions.md))
Call Pickup
Answer an extension that is currently ringing
Call Recordings
Record all calls, some calls or parts of the call
[Call Recordings](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/call_recordings.html)
Call Routing
Send the call to multiple directions or performactions based on caller id and other information (see [Dialplan Manager](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/dialplan/dialplan_manager.html))
[Call Routing](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/call_routing.html)
Call Announced Transfer
Transfer the active call to another internalor external call. Also known as a warm transfer
Call Blind Transfer
Transfer calls like a queue or IVR handoff
[Feature Codes](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/additional_information/feature_codes.html)
Call Transfer
General call transfer functionality
[Feature Codes](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/additional_information/feature_codes.html)
Call Waiting
Toggle between calls with a beep notification
[Feature Codes](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/additional_information/feature_codes.html)
Do Not Disturb (DND)
Direct calls to voicemail by defaultor send to an alternate destination
[Call Routing](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/call_routing.html)
Follow Me
Ring multiple extensions or external numbers
[Follow Me](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/follow_me.html)
Parking
Park calls on hold for pickup by another extension
[Parking](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/parking.html)
Queues
Load calls into queues to answer in join order
[Queues](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/queues.html)
Ring Groups
Ring multiple extensions from one extensionwith an option to receive emails on missed calls
[Ring Groups](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/ring_group.html)

## Conferencing[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#conferencing)
[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#conferencing)
Feature
Description
Documentation
Conference
Voice/video conference calls, optionally PIN-securedTransfer calls in with interactive conference controlsShow callers, manage volume, see talking status,options to kick/mute/unmute/deaf/undeaf members
[Conference](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/conference.html)
Conference Center
Unlimited rooms with moderation, PINs, and recording
[Conference Center](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/conference_center.html)

## Reports & Tools[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#reports-tools)
[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#reports-tools)
Feature
Description
Documentation
Call Detail Records
Detailed call reports, exportable to CSV
[Call Detail Records](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/call_detail_record.html)
Command
Execute commands and SQL queries via GUI
[Command](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/advanced/command.html)
Editor
Edit PHP, XML, and provisioning files
[Editor](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/advanced/editors.html)
Extension Summary
Show activity per domain, such as misssed callsanswered calls, no answer, inbound duration,outbound duration, amount of outbound/inbound callsand Average length of Conversation (ALOC)Export Summarized information as an CSV file
[Extension Summary](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/status/extension_summary.html)

## System Config[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#system-config)
[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#system-config)
Feature
Description
Documentation
Authentication
Web interface with plugin support (LDAP, AD)
Configuration
While the admin configures the system in the webinterface. The data is saved to the database andcan optionally be deliverd to FreeSWITCH via XML files, or on demand from the database
[Contacts](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/contacts.html)
Contacts
Manage your contacts. Import from Outlook CSV Export contacts to your cell phone with QR Codes Additional features such as time cards andinvoices that can be related to the contacts
Device Provisioning
Provision devices with contacts as phone directoriesEnable and disable vendors, Set memory,expansion (sidecars), and programmable keysSetup endpoints for Yealink, Polycom, Cisco, etc
[Device Provision](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/provision.html)
Dialplan Manager
The dialplan is used to setup call destinations basedon conditions and context. You can use thedialplan to send calls to gateways, auto attendants,external numbers, to scripts, or any destination
[Dialplan Manager](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/dialplan/dialplan_manager.html)
Gateways
Gateways provide access into other voice networksThese can be voice providers or other systemsthat require SIP registration. [See Video](https://youtu.be/YKOTACDYQ3A)
[Gateways](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/accounts/gateways.html)
Multi-Tenant
Domain based multi-tenant using subdomainse.g. red.pbxhosting.tld or blue.pbxhosting.tld
[Multi-Tenant](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/advanced/domains.html)
Scalable and Redundant
Configurable for multi-master database replication,file replication, FusionPBX, and FreeSWITCHMulti-server distribution for enterprise scalability
[Training](https://fusionpbx.com/training)
Manage Users/Groups
Manage permissions levels and users
[Group Manager](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/advanced/group_manager.html)

## Advanced Features[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#advanced-features)
[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#advanced-features)
Feature
Description
Documentation
Call Flows (Day/Night Mode)
To direct calls between two destinations.Direction can be displayed on phones BLF
Caller ID
Customize and support provider caller ID
Call Center
Create a robust call center environment
[Call Centers](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/call_center.html)
Dial by Name (*411)
Search extensions by first or last name
[Dial by Name](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/additional_information/dial_by_name.html)
Direct Inward System Access
Gives ability to call into the system, putin a pin code, and then call back outbound
[Dialplan Details](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/dialplan/dialplan_details.html#disa)
Extensions
Create extensions for phone registrationand options to send an email on missed calls to one or multiple contacts
[Extensions](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/accounts/extensions.html)
Fax Server
Send/receive faxes with advanced features
[Fax Server](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/fax_server.html)
Hot Desking
Login to another phone device to becomean extension temporarily or permanentlyAlso know as hoteling or extension mobility
Inbound/Outbound Call Routing
Routes to receive or send calls in or out
[Dialplans](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/dialplans.html)
IVR Menus (Auto Attendant)
Interactive voice prompts with TTS support
[IVR Menus](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/ivr.html)
Music on Hold
Allows multiple categories of music on hold that can be set globally or per domain. Caninject additional audio on intervals such as‘Your call is very important to usplease stand by’
[Music on Hold](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/music_on_hold.html)
Operator Panel
A virtual panel that agents can drag anddrop transfer calls. Set agents to available,on break, do not disturb and logged out
[Operator Panel](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/operator_panel.html)
Paging
Page extensions with optional password
[Dialplan Details](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/dialplan/dialplan_details.html#page)
Phrases
Use xml handler and xml from file systemyou can string together multiple voice files
[Phrases](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/phrases.html)
Provider Setup
Configure voice providers
Re-branding and Customize
With unprecedented customizability youcan meet your needs or the needs of yourcustomers. Customize themes, menus,and hundreds of theme adjustments
[Support](http://fusionpbx.com/support.php)
Recordings
Create and manage personalized recordings
[Recordings](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/recordings.html)
Time Conditions
Time-based call routing with domain,global options and holiday presets
[Time Conditions](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/time_conditions.html)
Voicemail
Advanced voicemail with email and IVR
[Voicemail](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/voicemail.html)
Voicemail to Email
Have voicemails sent to email
[Voicemail to Email](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#../getting_started/voicemail_to_email.md)
Voicemail Transcription
Convert voicemails to text
[Voicemail](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications/voicemail.html#voicemail-transcription)
WebRTC
Make/Receive video calls in a web browser
[WebRTC](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/applications_optional/webrtc.html)

## Additional Features[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#additional-features)
[](https://docs.fusionpbx.com/en/latest/features/features.html#additional-features)
This list is not exhaustive—FusionPBX offers many more capabilities. Stay tuned as we expand this documentation!
